": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my God! With what has passed of it, the month of fasting has become one half It is going to complete and end However, I have no good deeds to offer to You except for my faith in You and my hope of You My hope is weakened by my sincere fear of You However, my faith shall not be weakened near You with Your granting me success.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ قَدِ انْتَصَفَ شَهْرُ الصِّيَامِ بِمَا مَضٰى مِنْ اَيَّامِهٖ وَانْجَذَبَ اِلٰى تَمَامِهٖ وَاخْتِتَامِهٖ وَمَا لِيْ عُدَّةٌ اَعْتَدُّ بِهَا فَاَلْجَاُ اِلَيْهَا وَلَا اَعْمَالٌ مِنَ الصَّالِحَاتِ اُعَوِّلُ عَلَيْهَا سِوٰى اِيْمَانِيْ بِكَ وَرَجَاۗئِيْ لَكَ فَاَمَّا رَجَاۗئِيْ فَيُكَدِّرُهٗ عَلَيَّ صَفْوَةُ الْخَوْفِ مِنْكَ وَاَمَّا اِيْمَانِيْ فَلَا يَضِيْعُ عِنْدَكَ وَهُوَ بِتَوْفِيْقِكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null